Important source-data notice:
Original scientific papers, parsed source text, figures, evidence quotes, and any MinerU-derived source samples remain governed by the licenses of their original publications. Each dataset record preserves source metadata in `source.license`, `source.doi`, and related fields. Users are responsible for respecting the original source licenses when redistributing or reusing source text.

